ount.</td></tr></tbody></table>\\n\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/node-client/public/get_account_balances.mdx#parameters\",\"isPage\":false,\"text\":\"\\nParameterLocationTypeRequiredDescriptionaddressqueryAddresstrueThe wallet address that owns the account.\\n\",\"title\":\"Parameters\",\"titles\":[null,null,\"Get Account Balances\"]},{\"href\":\"/node-client/public/get_account_balances#response\",\"html\":\"\\n<table><thead><tr><th>Status</th><th>Meaning</th><th>Schema</th><th>Description</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>200</code></td><td><a href=\\\"/types/ok\\\">OK</a></td><td><a href=\\\"/types/coin\\\">Coin</a> ⛁</td><td>The response containing all account balances.</td></tr><tr><td><code>400</code></td><td><a href=\\\"/types/bad-request\\\">Bad Request</a></td><td></td><td>The request was malformed or invalid.</td></tr></tbody></table>\\n<p>Examples: <a href=\\\"https://github.com/dydxprotocol/v4-clients/blob/3e8c7e1b960291b7ef273962d374d9934a5c4d33/v4-client-py-v2/examples/validator_get_example.py#L20\\\">Python</a> | <a href=\\\"https://github.com/dydxprotocol/v4-clients/blob/3e8c7e1b960291b7ef273962d374d9934a5c4d33/v4-client-js/examples/validator_get_example.ts#L17\\\">TypeScript</a> | <a href=\\\"https://github.com/dydxprotocol/v4-clients/blob/3e8c7e1b960291b7ef273962d374d9934a5c4d33/v4-client-rs/client/examples/validator_get.rs#L35o\\\">Rust</a> | <a href=\\\"https://test-dydx-rest.kingnodes.com/cosmos/bank/v1beta1/balances/dydx14zzueazeh0hj67cghhf9jypslcf9sh2n5k6art\\\">API</a> | <a href=\\\"../../interaction/data/accounts#get-account-balances\\\">Guide - Get Account Balances</a></p>\",\"id\":\"docs/pages/node-client/public/get_account_balances.mdx#response\",\"isPage\":false,\"text\":\"\\nStatusMeaningSchemaDescription200OKCoin ⛁The response containing all account balances.400Bad RequestThe request was malformed or invalid.\\nExamples: Python | TypeScript | Rust | API | Guide - Get Account Balances\",\"title\":\"Response\",\"titles\":[null,null,\"Get Acco